        Clause 24 [<span class="italic">Interpretation</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05148'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_245' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
