        <q>Page 23, line 45, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) "Accessibility strategy" and "accessibility plan" have the meaning given in section 28D.").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05150'>
