          <p class='first-para'>
            Before my noble friend decides what to do, I thank the Minister very much for her comments. Does she also agree that the question of support workers is vital for those in HE Perhaps institutions might be willing to take on&#x2014;
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0621P0-05189'>
