          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0621P0-05276'>
        <a name='S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_373'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-james-erskine-1' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_373' title='Link to this speech by Mr James Erskine' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-erskine-1" title="Mr James Erskine">The Earl of Mar and Kellie</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
