      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05343'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_440' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 3 [<span class="italic">Responsible Bodies for Educational Institutions</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05344'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_441' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Blackstone</span> moved Amendment No. 214:
        <q>Schedule 3, page 39, line 19, leave out ("section") and insert ("sector").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05345'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_442' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05346'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_443' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 3, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05347'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_444' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 4 [<span class="italic">Modifications of Chapter II of Part IV of the 1995 Act</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05348'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_445' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Blackstone</span> moved Amendments Nos. 215 and 216:
        <q>Schedule 4, page 40, line 41, leave out ("terms on") and insert ("services").</q>
        <q>Schedule 4, page 40, line 42, after ("provide-) insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) "Services", in relation to a course, means").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05349'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_446' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendments agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05350'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_447' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 217 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05351'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_448' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Blackstone</span> moved Amendments Nos. 218 and 219:
        <q>Schedule 4, page 42, line 16, leave out ("terms on") and insert ("services").</q>
        <q>Schedule 4, page 42, line 16, after second ("provide") insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) "Services", in relation to a course, means").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05352'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_449' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendments agreed to.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_283gc' title='Col. 283GC &mdash; HL Deb 06 February 2001 vol 621 c283GC' name='column_283gc' href='#column_283gc' rel='bookmark'>283GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05353'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_450' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 4, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05354'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_451' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedules 5 and 6 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05355'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_452' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 7 [<span class="italic">Minor and Consequential Amendments</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05356'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_453' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 220 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05357'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_454' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 7 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05358'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_455' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Remaining schedule agreed to.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_284gc' title='Col. 284GC &mdash; HL Deb 06 February 2001 vol 621 c284GC' name='column_284gc' href='#column_284gc' rel='bookmark'>284GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05359'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_456' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Title agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0621P0-05360'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_457' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported with amendments.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0621P0-05361'>
        <a name='S5LV0621P0_20010206_GCR_458'>  </a>
